release_notes:
This release is a hotfix for 2022.5.310.0.
## Notable updates
 
- Fixed a crash from reading /etc/resolv.conf while it was being updated
- Removed large memory leak causing ~1GB/day memory growth
- Bug fixes and connection stability improvement
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
 
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
